WEBVTT

01:53.280 --> 01:57.390
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.630 --> 02:01.900
[Episode 17]

02:05.040 --> 02:06.150
Your Excellency.

02:06.170 --> 02:07.710
Your Excellency,
you've found a solution?

02:07.710 --> 02:10.110
Do we no longer
have to wait until next year?

02:11.580 --> 02:14.400
"Misfortune may turn out
to be a blessing in disguise."

02:14.400 --> 02:15.860
Teacher Ping told me that,

02:16.110 --> 02:18.050
based on precedents set
by the late governor,

02:18.050 --> 02:19.910
there may be a way to resolve this.

02:22.240 --> 02:23.000
Really?

02:27.190 --> 02:29.250
Precepts on the Founding of a City...

02:31.760 --> 02:34.280
Within it, there is a method
called recommendation,

02:34.280 --> 02:35.800
allowing gifted individuals
to be promoted beyond rank

02:35.800 --> 02:37.320
and serve as officials of the Nine Cities.

02:37.320 --> 02:37.980
Take a look.

02:46.920 --> 02:47.880
Here it is. Here.

02:50.400 --> 02:51.430
That's great.

02:56.310 --> 02:57.030
But

02:57.560 --> 02:59.680
the selection exam has only just begun.

02:59.680 --> 03:01.040
Why don't we wait...

03:01.590 --> 03:03.030
wait until the results are announced

03:03.030 --> 03:04.690
before making any decisions?

03:05.260 --> 03:05.790
Alright,

03:06.360 --> 03:07.280
it's up to you.

03:08.900 --> 03:09.700
Are you happy?

03:14.300 --> 03:16.130
The first exam is over;

03:16.160 --> 03:18.170
the second is about to start.

04:11.040 --> 04:13.310
-The gate is opening.
-The gate is opening.

04:13.310 --> 04:15.710
-They're coming out.
-They're coming out.

04:17.870 --> 04:18.680
They are out.

04:19.760 --> 04:21.370
-How did it go?
-Just like that.

04:21.040 --> 04:22.430
[Examination Academy]

04:27.940 --> 04:28.940
I'm here!

04:30.250 --> 04:31.490
Finally out.

04:31.520 --> 04:32.370
How did it go?

04:32.670 --> 04:33.670
How did you all do?

04:35.300 --> 04:36.510
Well...

04:36.530 --> 04:39.390
It's already been submitted.
No point saying more.

04:39.630 --> 04:40.800
So what were

04:40.820 --> 04:42.220
the questions this time?

04:42.270 --> 04:43.120
They were drawn
from the Current Affairs Essay,

04:43.120 --> 04:44.890
focusing on people's governance
and official governance.

04:44.890 --> 04:45.680
How did everyone answer?

04:45.680 --> 04:47.460
Of course,
governing the people comes first.

04:47.460 --> 04:49.270
This Current Affairs Essay question

04:49.270 --> 04:50.870
came from a top-scoring essay

04:50.870 --> 04:52.230
in a selection exam a few years ago.

04:52.230 --> 04:53.540
I've already memorized it completely.

04:53.540 --> 04:56.050
The core idea of the original text
is simply governing the people.

04:56.050 --> 04:58.320
Looks like I've got this in the bag, then.

04:59.600 --> 05:01.220
If you ask me,

05:01.760 --> 05:04.450
I lean toward
governing the officials first.

05:04.730 --> 05:06.560
Only by properly supervising officials

05:06.560 --> 05:09.120
can the people truly benefit.

05:09.520 --> 05:11.620
My teacher told me something
similar before,

05:11.620 --> 05:12.570
so I answered

05:12.600 --> 05:14.530
"governing the officials first."

05:15.210 --> 05:16.060
That's great.

05:16.810 --> 05:18.070
Let's head back first.

05:18.240 --> 05:18.770
Let's go.

05:53.409 --> 05:54.409
Your Excellency,

05:55.430 --> 05:57.120
I believe this essay

05:57.120 --> 06:00.120
is ranked third
in this year's Current Affairs Essay.

06:04.180 --> 06:05.640
I agree, Your Excellency.

06:13.390 --> 06:14.800
Great minds think alike.

06:16.390 --> 06:17.790
What about second place?

06:18.840 --> 06:20.480
The remaining two essays

06:20.510 --> 06:24.230
take two completely different directions
in their arguments.

06:24.710 --> 06:25.860
I believe

06:25.880 --> 06:28.410
this one on governing
the people is superior,

06:28.520 --> 06:31.270
and it also aligns more closely
with Nine Cities' long-standing policies.

06:31.270 --> 06:32.740
As long as the people
don't cause trouble,

06:32.740 --> 06:34.800
Nine Cities won't have any problems.

06:38.190 --> 06:41.040
This selection exam
is different from the past;

06:41.290 --> 06:42.550
it marks the beginning

06:42.750 --> 06:45.480
of admitting commoners
and sets a new precedent.

06:46.290 --> 06:47.370
These commoners

06:48.270 --> 06:51.159
come from streets and villages,

06:51.840 --> 06:54.040
and they understand the people deeply.

06:54.870 --> 06:55.430
Naturally,

06:55.430 --> 06:58.510
they are more familiar with the principles
of governing the people.

06:58.510 --> 07:00.400
Lord Zheng, your certainty

07:00.570 --> 07:02.130
may be somewhat one-sided.

07:05.120 --> 07:06.850
Now that commoners

07:07.310 --> 07:09.040
are entering the bureaucracy,

07:09.160 --> 07:10.190
I believe

07:11.500 --> 07:12.970
Nine Cities

07:13.070 --> 07:15.000
should impose stricter oversight

07:15.360 --> 07:16.960
on officials going forward.

07:17.240 --> 07:19.450
Therefore, the essay
on governing officials

07:19.450 --> 07:20.450
is better.

07:22.070 --> 07:24.360
I agree with Zheng.

07:25.150 --> 07:26.830
Compared to the other,

07:26.850 --> 07:29.450
the essay on governing officials
is superior.

07:32.190 --> 07:34.430
Governing officials benefits the people

07:34.430 --> 07:36.070
and is indeed

07:37.350 --> 07:38.820
the best choice,

07:39.690 --> 07:40.950
worthy of first place.

07:49.440 --> 07:50.560
Grandfather,

07:50.720 --> 07:51.720
I'm heading out.

07:52.870 --> 07:54.510
Wait, wait, wait—hold on.

07:55.390 --> 07:56.360
Shi,

08:00.450 --> 08:02.310
are you planning to go see the results

08:02.310 --> 08:04.070
like that this morning?

08:04.090 --> 08:05.630
Then what else am I supposed to do?

08:05.630 --> 08:07.460
I have prepared

08:07.820 --> 08:10.620
the three essentials
for you to check the results.

08:11.270 --> 08:12.560
First essential—

08:15.010 --> 08:16.890
mugwort brushing your face,

08:19.430 --> 08:21.630
so your gaze becomes as sharp as a torch.

08:24.800 --> 08:25.970
Second essential—

08:26.000 --> 08:26.480
come,

08:27.800 --> 08:29.470
wash your hands with mugwort,

08:30.590 --> 08:32.200
ensuring you succeed the moment

08:32.200 --> 08:33.360
you see the results.

08:34.990 --> 08:36.200
Third essential—

08:40.840 --> 08:42.570
mugwort to soothe your throat,

08:43.200 --> 08:45.750
so when you return home with good news,

08:46.600 --> 08:48.600
your words will ring loud and clear.

08:49.840 --> 08:50.960
Master.

08:53.480 --> 08:54.200
Uncle Yi,

08:54.870 --> 08:56.800
pass me Grandfather's breakfast.

08:56.930 --> 08:57.710
Grandfather,

08:57.710 --> 08:59.070
look at you—

08:59.100 --> 09:00.190
you got up so early
preparing all this for me

09:00.190 --> 09:02.000
that you didn't even have time to eat.

09:02.000 --> 09:03.480
I really can't bear it.

09:03.510 --> 09:05.480
Let me serve you breakfast first.

09:08.270 --> 09:09.330
As for the results...
I might as well not go check them.

09:09.330 --> 09:10.050
No, no, no.

09:10.290 --> 09:11.690
My grandson must be

09:11.720 --> 09:13.580
the very first to see the results!

09:14.490 --> 09:15.290
Yes, yes, yes—

09:15.300 --> 09:16.130
seize the top rank,

09:16.130 --> 09:17.130
strike first!

09:17.160 --> 09:19.240
Even being first to see the results
matters too.

09:19.240 --> 09:20.040
Yes, yes, yes.

09:21.670 --> 09:23.630
I'm leaving Grandfather in your care.

09:23.630 --> 09:24.480
As for you—

09:25.030 --> 09:26.270
drink this first.

09:30.790 --> 09:31.550
Shi.

09:31.910 --> 09:33.030
Shi!

09:37.240 --> 09:39.050
He's bound to make the list anyway.

09:39.050 --> 09:40.290
Of course.

09:41.430 --> 09:42.430
Go on, drink it.

09:44.200 --> 09:46.600
-The results are out!
-The results are out!

09:47.970 --> 09:49.760
Young Master! Young Master!

09:49.780 --> 09:51.580
First place—Tian Xing!

09:52.480 --> 09:52.960
Let's go!

09:52.960 --> 09:54.160
Hurry and take a look!

09:59.440 --> 10:00.360
First place!

10:00.800 --> 10:02.400
It really is Tian Xing.

10:02.510 --> 10:03.840
You came in first!

10:03.840 --> 10:05.440
Looks like we can celebrate.

10:08.000 --> 10:09.790
Young Master, second place—

10:09.790 --> 10:11.000
Wei Rong!

10:12.040 --> 10:13.940
Can you stop coming back
like something
that only moves

10:13.940 --> 10:15.840
when it‘s pushed,
reporting one name at a time?

10:15.840 --> 10:16.960
Wei Rong

10:17.090 --> 10:18.690
really got in.

10:20.050 --> 10:21.050
Where is Wei Rong?

10:21.770 --> 10:22.980
I'm here.

10:23.010 --> 10:23.890
Wei Rong,

10:23.910 --> 10:25.500
you came in second.

10:25.550 --> 10:27.170
Just as expected, I suppose.

10:27.750 --> 10:28.360
Nothing more

10:28.360 --> 10:30.260
than an empty name
I use to buy my freedom.

10:30.260 --> 10:31.690
Now go and tell me

10:31.720 --> 10:32.660
the next ten rankings,

10:32.660 --> 10:33.590
or you're fired!

10:33.910 --> 10:35.080
Right away.

10:44.440 --> 10:45.270
Third place...

10:45.270 --> 10:46.320
Twenty-third place?

10:46.320 --> 10:47.200
Bo Qin.

10:49.200 --> 10:51.060
Congratulations, Young Master!

10:53.360 --> 10:54.890
Second Young Master Zheng,

10:54.960 --> 10:56.120
with your learning,

10:56.910 --> 10:58.970
how did you end up only twenty-third?

11:00.270 --> 11:01.630
Help!

11:03.790 --> 11:04.870
What's going on over there?

11:04.870 --> 11:05.720
Let's go take a look!

11:05.720 --> 11:07.220
Is there a doctor?

11:07.300 --> 11:08.330
Someone help!

11:08.390 --> 11:09.960
-My young master's in critical condition!
-Please make way!

11:09.960 --> 11:10.790
What happened?

11:10.790 --> 11:11.960
H-He just suddenly collapsed.

11:11.960 --> 11:13.240
Come on, help him up.

11:13.910 --> 11:15.390
You... can you manage?

11:16.720 --> 11:17.520
Young Master.

11:18.320 --> 11:19.450
How is he, Tian Xing?

11:22.840 --> 11:23.320
What...

11:23.670 --> 11:24.600
what's going on?

11:29.580 --> 11:30.630
He's awake! He's awake!

11:30.630 --> 11:31.390
He's out of danger now.

11:31.390 --> 11:32.200
He's awake.

11:32.200 --> 11:33.200
Move aside.

11:33.440 --> 11:34.200
What are you doing?

11:34.200 --> 11:35.400
You stole my top rank,

11:35.720 --> 11:37.790
and you still dare to show
your face in front of me?

11:37.790 --> 11:38.030
This...

11:38.030 --> 11:40.080
From now on,
all of you better watch yourselves.

11:40.080 --> 11:41.240
How can you be like this?

11:41.240 --> 11:41.870
Young Master! Young Master!

11:41.870 --> 11:43.670
He clearly just saved your life.

11:59.240 --> 12:00.640
Looks like he's okay now.

12:03.840 --> 12:05.390
Second Young Master Zheng,

12:05.420 --> 12:06.190
have you

12:06.210 --> 12:08.480
thought about how
you're going to explain this

12:08.480 --> 12:10.140
to Lord Zheng when you go back?

12:20.930 --> 12:21.850
Master,

12:21.880 --> 12:25.000
this is the list of newly admitted
scholars sent by the Examination Office.

12:25.000 --> 12:25.510
Come on. Come on.

12:25.510 --> 12:26.970
Pass it to me. Pass it to me.

12:36.720 --> 12:38.240
Is this really accurate?

12:38.630 --> 12:39.600
It is.

12:43.570 --> 12:44.810
Twenty-third place!

13:52.700 --> 13:53.780
Master,

13:54.230 --> 13:56.960
Young Master Shi personally cooked you
a bowl of noodles

13:56.960 --> 13:58.720
because he knew you hadn't had dinner.

13:58.720 --> 13:59.960
He asked me to bring it over for you.

13:59.960 --> 14:01.080
Throw it away.

14:01.080 --> 14:01.910
I'm not eating.

14:01.910 --> 14:02.530
Yes.

14:04.100 --> 14:05.130
Wait.

15:48.790 --> 15:49.670
Grand...

15:51.000 --> 15:52.960
I told you to go back to sleep.

15:53.790 --> 15:54.590
Grandfather.

15:55.580 --> 15:58.200
Why are you still kneeling here?

15:58.600 --> 16:01.730
Our ancestors already
understand your intentions.

16:01.970 --> 16:04.700
I know I've failed
the Zheng family's ancestors,

16:04.850 --> 16:07.000
and I've failed you even more,
Grandfather.

16:07.000 --> 16:09.450
Grandfather, the more you hesitate
to punish me,

16:09.450 --> 16:11.450
the more I feel I must punish myself.

16:14.330 --> 16:16.610
What good is self-punishment?

16:18.150 --> 16:20.360
Can it change your ranking?

16:21.390 --> 16:23.190
Tell me—what were you thinking?

16:24.150 --> 16:25.320
Out of

16:26.510 --> 16:28.240
22 newly admitted scholars,

16:29.150 --> 16:30.030
you still

16:31.020 --> 16:32.050
came in the 23rd.

16:34.320 --> 16:37.320
You study every day
in the Education Bureau—

16:37.390 --> 16:39.790
what happened to all that learning?

16:42.030 --> 16:43.000
Tomorrow,

16:43.960 --> 16:47.620
all the newly admitted scholars
will attend the morning meeting,

16:47.750 --> 16:49.720
yet my most beloved grandson

16:50.280 --> 16:53.280
won't even have the qualification to go.

16:53.300 --> 16:56.020
How am I supposed
to face people after this?

16:58.960 --> 17:00.890
Perhaps I truly lack talent

17:01.600 --> 17:03.800
and am not meant for an official career.

17:03.870 --> 17:05.319
Ancestors above...

17:05.790 --> 17:07.240
How did I raise

17:07.240 --> 17:09.349
such an unambitious child?

17:10.310 --> 17:12.560
But don't worry—

17:12.920 --> 17:14.380
this year didn't work out,

17:15.160 --> 17:16.619
we'll try again next year.

17:19.160 --> 17:20.160
And what if...

17:20.930 --> 17:22.530
I still can't pass next year?

17:24.960 --> 17:26.960
You're going to make me die of anger!

17:27.790 --> 17:28.720
I wouldn't dare.

17:34.440 --> 17:35.440
Tomorrow...

17:36.150 --> 17:36.950
you...

17:36.970 --> 17:38.170
Starting tomorrow,

17:38.270 --> 17:40.000
we're not go anywhere.

17:41.720 --> 17:42.340
Let's

17:42.610 --> 17:45.200
report to the Education Bureau
every single day.

17:45.200 --> 17:46.400
If it doesn't work this year,

17:46.400 --> 17:47.800
there's still next year.

17:48.000 --> 17:49.350
If next year fails,

17:49.350 --> 17:51.280
there's still the year after that.

17:52.640 --> 17:53.480
Get up

17:54.310 --> 17:55.440
and go back to sleep.

17:57.270 --> 17:58.880
Even if you kneel here

17:58.880 --> 18:00.680
until your knees are ruined

18:00.820 --> 18:03.470
and can't walk
to the Education Bureau tomorrow,

18:03.470 --> 18:05.000
I'll have Zheng Yi carry you

18:05.780 --> 18:07.900
to the Education Bureau if I have to.

18:11.620 --> 18:12.280
Alright,

18:12.830 --> 18:16.560
I'll report to the Education Bureau
first thing tomorrow morning.

18:31.650 --> 18:34.010
[Carriage Stop Gate]

18:36.970 --> 18:39.610
♪ Our hearts reach for the morning glow ♪

18:39.790 --> 18:43.240
♪ Our dreams fear no barren land below ♪

18:43.890 --> 18:48.990
♪ What does it matter
if we fly against the wind? ♪

18:49.420 --> 18:52.000
♪ We vow to live up
to our youthful prime ♪

18:52.260 --> 18:56.080
♪ To walk alongside ordinary folks alike ♪

18:56.640 --> 18:59.580
♪ Sharing the same ray of light ♪

18:59.750 --> 19:05.280
♪ Fear no strange land nor dim twilight ♪

19:05.450 --> 19:08.520
♪ All for this boundless world ♪

19:08.540 --> 19:13.650
♪ To wear a robe of radiant glory ♪

19:15.060 --> 19:20.650
♪ Face the light,
gaze ahead with brave eyes ♪

19:20.830 --> 19:25.030
♪ Let all darkness and hurt step aside ♪

19:25.050 --> 19:27.180
♪ It's unstoppable ♪

19:27.380 --> 19:33.080
♪ Chase the light,
let our dreams unfold wide ♪

19:33.190 --> 19:37.420
♪ With bold resolve, ignite plain faith ♪

19:37.400 --> 19:38.640
What was that sound?

19:37.440 --> 19:39.310
♪ Light them up ♪

19:39.330 --> 19:43.060
♪ Let all wind and frost of days gone by ♪

19:42.160 --> 19:43.440
Judging by the sound...

19:43.200 --> 19:49.280
♪ Turn to countless beams
of light within my eye ♪

19:43.440 --> 19:45.300
It sounds like the Petition Drum.

19:45.350 --> 19:46.700
The Petition Drum?

19:48.900 --> 19:49.980
Your Excellency,

19:49.300 --> 19:55.560
♪ Await the sight of you ♪

19:50.000 --> 19:51.160
since the founding of the city,

19:51.160 --> 19:52.830
the Petition Drum has never been struck.

19:52.830 --> 19:54.270
Now that it has been sounded,

19:54.270 --> 19:55.790
no matter what you are doing,

19:55.790 --> 19:58.190
you must go
and hear the petition in person.

20:02.000 --> 20:03.590
Who is beating the drum?

20:04.890 --> 20:05.720
Fan Yun.

20:20.830 --> 20:24.830
Lord Jiang, are you proposing
to recommend Fan Yun for an official post?

20:25.920 --> 20:26.880
That is correct.

20:28.350 --> 20:29.750
Then why did the two of you

20:29.920 --> 20:31.610
suddenly think of

20:32.520 --> 20:34.060
beating the Petition Drum?

20:34.350 --> 20:36.610
I would never act without solid grounds.

20:36.680 --> 20:37.970
I would never

20:38.410 --> 20:40.010
act on something uncertain.

20:46.160 --> 20:47.960
I respect you, the Three Elders.

20:48.210 --> 20:49.120
I know

20:49.450 --> 20:51.340
you have all worked tirelessly

20:51.370 --> 20:52.560
on the reform of the selection exam,

20:52.560 --> 20:53.510
and have already

20:53.540 --> 20:55.340
made the greatest concessions.

20:56.350 --> 20:57.330
So,

20:57.720 --> 20:58.930
after learning

20:59.030 --> 21:01.330
that the proposal to allow women
to take the selection exam had failed,

21:01.330 --> 21:02.660
I harbor no complaints.

21:05.020 --> 21:06.080
During this time,

21:06.270 --> 21:08.800
I searched through
many historical records,

21:09.030 --> 21:09.830
and finally

21:12.440 --> 21:13.750
found a solution

21:14.240 --> 21:15.720
in this book.

21:15.980 --> 21:16.660
This...

21:23.370 --> 21:23.960
This...

21:26.370 --> 21:27.610
In this book—

21:27.640 --> 21:28.840
Chapter 7,

21:28.860 --> 21:29.690
Section 5,

21:29.920 --> 21:31.160
Line 36,

21:32.040 --> 21:33.170
footnote at the end:

21:33.840 --> 21:35.800
if one renders merit for the city,

21:36.030 --> 21:37.280
regardless of age

21:37.370 --> 21:38.360
or status,

21:38.840 --> 21:40.470
they may be exceptionally promoted

21:40.470 --> 21:41.340
and recommended

21:41.340 --> 21:42.670
into official service.

21:50.030 --> 21:51.150
The text says

21:51.320 --> 21:52.450
"regardless of age,

21:52.720 --> 21:54.050
regardless of status,"

21:54.490 --> 21:56.730
but it does not mention gender.

21:57.900 --> 22:00.100
Moreover, during this selection exam,

22:00.750 --> 22:02.660
Fan Yun actively contributed advice

22:02.660 --> 22:04.750
and protected the candidates' exam token

22:04.750 --> 22:07.160
from the blades
of the Shadow Slay League,

22:07.960 --> 22:10.420
ensuring the selection exam
could proceed smoothly.

22:10.420 --> 22:11.340
I believe

22:11.780 --> 22:13.780
she deserves great credit for this.

22:15.140 --> 22:17.820
Previously, officials were divided

22:17.850 --> 22:19.850
on whether women
could serve as officials.

22:19.850 --> 22:22.320
Why not let Fan Yun
serve as a test case?

22:23.470 --> 22:27.530
If it proves inappropriate, then
the matter need not be discussed again.

22:30.160 --> 22:31.020
I believe

22:31.390 --> 22:33.050
Lord Jiang makes a fair point.

22:33.750 --> 22:34.550
Three Elders,

22:34.980 --> 22:36.020
what do you think?

22:41.830 --> 22:43.160
Even though Fan Yun

22:44.200 --> 22:46.510
has rendered such merit,

22:46.510 --> 22:49.680
whether it is sufficient

22:50.640 --> 22:52.700
still requires further discussion.

22:53.720 --> 22:55.900
At this critical moment of reform,

22:57.330 --> 22:58.790
safeguarding new decrees

22:59.440 --> 23:01.200
and protecting the people's safety

23:01.200 --> 23:02.530
is indeed a great merit.

23:04.110 --> 23:05.440
This is worth a try.

23:16.010 --> 23:16.780
Fan Yun,

23:18.090 --> 23:18.820
in that case,

23:19.480 --> 23:21.470
I permit you to serve

23:22.400 --> 23:24.870
as a probationary official
and undergo trial appointment

23:24.870 --> 23:26.830
together with the newly admitted scholars.

23:26.830 --> 23:28.410
♪ Spring winds, autumn rain ♪

23:28.430 --> 23:29.940
♪ Flowers bloom for a single season ♪

23:29.990 --> 23:32.080
♪ Fallen petals turn into mud ♪

23:32.100 --> 23:34.060
♪ Nurturing all living things ♪

23:32.770 --> 23:34.370
Thank you, Your Excellency.

23:34.760 --> 23:37.380
♪ Never once asking for
even a single cent ♪

23:38.780 --> 23:41.140
♪ Yet willing, in the name of the clouds ♪

23:41.170 --> 23:42.750
♪ To ignite myself ♪

23:42.780 --> 23:44.810
♪ For the people under heaven ♪

23:45.100 --> 23:47.340
♪ Bright moon, clear breeze ♪

23:45.720 --> 23:49.350
Summon the first three candidates
to enter the hall.

23:47.360 --> 23:51.320
♪ Accompany a heart without dust ♪

23:52.160 --> 23:53.730
♪ All the noise and chaos ♪

23:53.750 --> 23:55.410
♪ The rises and falls of life ♪

23:55.430 --> 23:57.390
♪ What does hardship matter? ♪

23:57.420 --> 23:59.830
♪ In the moment of looking back ♪

23:58.070 --> 23:59.240
I, Tian Xing...

23:59.240 --> 24:00.750
I, Bo Qin...

24:00.050 --> 24:03.420
♪ This life is worth it ♪

24:01.790 --> 24:03.960
-Pay my respects to Your Excellency.
-Pay my respects to Your Excellency.

24:03.690 --> 24:06.200
♪ When longing for dawn ♪

24:03.960 --> 24:05.270
All esteemed candidates, rise.

24:05.270 --> 24:06.480
Thank you, Your Excellency.

24:06.220 --> 24:10.090
♪ Who are the dream-walkers? ♪

24:07.720 --> 24:10.680
Second-place candidate Wei Rong
reports illness

24:10.110 --> 24:12.380
♪ Facing the light ♪

24:10.680 --> 24:13.000
and is therefore unable
to attend the hall.

24:12.650 --> 24:16.340
♪ Singing a long song along the way ♪

24:13.000 --> 24:13.920
Continue.

24:13.920 --> 24:18.550
Summon Fan Yun, the provisional official,
to enter the hall.

24:16.370 --> 24:18.950
♪ I am willing to become ♪

24:18.970 --> 24:20.590
♪ A long-lasting lantern ♪

24:20.620 --> 24:22.660
♪ Lighting the path ahead ♪

24:22.680 --> 24:25.160
♪ Bypassing right and wrong ♪

24:25.200 --> 24:28.910
♪ Prejudice and fanaticism ♪

24:28.930 --> 24:31.640
♪ Until this road ♪

24:31.680 --> 24:33.370
♪ Has no more obstacles ♪

24:33.390 --> 24:35.550
♪ Time flows like water ♪

24:35.570 --> 24:42.070
♪ Not wasting years of perseverance ♪

24:50.530 --> 24:52.730
I, Fan Yun,

24:52.750 --> 24:54.750
pay my respects to Your Excellency.

24:56.160 --> 24:57.030
Fan Yun, rise.

24:57.750 --> 24:59.160
Thank you, Your Excellency.

24:59.160 --> 25:03.460
♪ As long as the heart's light remains ♪

25:03.900 --> 25:13.270
♪ There won't be loneliness ♪

25:09.690 --> 25:11.380
[Taiji Palace]

25:11.600 --> 25:12.660
By tradition,

25:12.800 --> 25:15.310
shouldn't we go greet
the newly admitted scholars?

25:15.310 --> 25:16.510
Let's go. Let's go.

25:17.520 --> 25:19.920
Do you still not
see the situation clearly?

25:20.070 --> 25:22.070
Are you trying to go against Lord Zheng?

25:22.070 --> 25:23.000
I wouldn't dare.

25:23.510 --> 25:24.550
Besides,

25:25.160 --> 25:28.420
not all of them are proper
newly admitted scholars anyway.

25:33.550 --> 25:34.480
Zhao, isn't that

25:35.350 --> 25:38.010
the future consort of the governor
you personally selected back then?

25:38.010 --> 25:39.780
What's wrong with me

25:39.800 --> 25:41.130
going over to greet her?

25:41.790 --> 25:43.320
It's an expedient measure.

25:43.730 --> 25:46.410
Before these young ones
have firmly established themselves,

25:46.410 --> 25:48.340
we shouldn't get too close to them.

25:48.710 --> 25:51.110
That would be
the best protection for them.

25:52.680 --> 25:53.480
Let's go.

25:53.510 --> 25:54.640
Speaking of which,

25:54.660 --> 25:56.240
on such an important day,

25:57.540 --> 25:59.100
why isn't Wei Rong here?

25:59.480 --> 26:00.070
Right—

26:01.030 --> 26:02.030
where is Wei Rong?

26:03.540 --> 26:04.620
Lord Fan.

26:06.270 --> 26:08.510
His Excellency requests your presence.

26:08.510 --> 26:09.660
The Governor?

26:10.830 --> 26:11.920
I'll go over first.

26:28.110 --> 26:29.240
Your Excellency...

26:34.400 --> 26:35.400
Your Excellency?

26:38.420 --> 26:39.640
He called me here,

26:40.320 --> 26:41.940
yet he's not even here.

26:47.410 --> 26:49.060
The selection exam paper?

26:56.170 --> 26:58.570
They really are the selection exam papers.

27:13.210 --> 27:14.690
Y-Your Excellency.

27:17.600 --> 27:19.530
Do I really frighten you that much?

27:23.960 --> 27:24.800
No,

27:25.180 --> 27:26.820
I was just thinking

27:26.850 --> 27:28.000
about Wei Rong's

27:28.030 --> 27:29.310
absence earlier.

27:31.580 --> 27:32.520
Your Excellency,

27:32.520 --> 27:34.520
why don't you seem surprised at all?

27:35.350 --> 27:36.160
A few days ago,

27:36.760 --> 27:38.120
I already saw Wei Rong.

27:38.860 --> 27:40.190
He resigned from office

27:40.420 --> 27:42.010
and went off to live freely and carefree.

27:42.010 --> 27:42.730
Resign...

27:42.770 --> 27:43.530
What?

27:45.030 --> 27:46.750
He claimed illness
and resigned from office.

27:46.750 --> 27:49.350
That way, he avoids criticism
from Lord Zheng.

27:49.740 --> 27:51.600
Wei Rong has always been carefree

27:51.600 --> 27:52.850
and unconstrained;

27:53.550 --> 27:56.280
serving as an official would
only have bound him.

27:56.550 --> 27:59.410
It also spares those old pedants
the eyesore of him.

28:02.720 --> 28:03.980
But you—

28:04.880 --> 28:06.280
whenever you're with me,

28:06.690 --> 28:08.890
you always end up talking about others.

28:12.090 --> 28:13.370
It's been a long time

28:13.480 --> 28:14.750
since I last saw you.

28:15.070 --> 28:16.230
Don't you have anything

28:16.230 --> 28:17.440
you want to say to me?

28:22.250 --> 28:23.160
I...

28:26.560 --> 28:27.300
Right,

28:27.640 --> 28:29.000
there is something.

28:31.130 --> 28:32.320
I couldn't give it

28:32.970 --> 28:34.620
to Your Excellency
in the main hall earlier,

28:34.620 --> 28:35.580
so

28:37.090 --> 28:38.620
I'm returning it to you now.

28:42.290 --> 28:43.160
Anything else?

28:44.640 --> 28:45.770
A-Anything else...

28:48.160 --> 28:49.240
Anything else...

28:51.330 --> 28:52.190
One more thing.

28:53.330 --> 28:54.570
Although

28:54.600 --> 28:57.110
I was granted
an exceptional recommendation,

28:57.110 --> 28:58.510
rest assured, Your Excellency,

28:58.510 --> 28:59.800
I will do my utmost

28:59.820 --> 29:01.380
in the days ahead,

29:01.410 --> 29:02.400
live up to expectations,

29:02.400 --> 29:04.930
and wholeheartedly assist Your Excellency.

29:09.550 --> 29:10.350
You may leave.

29:13.090 --> 29:14.140
Since you call

29:14.720 --> 29:15.920
yourself my subject,

29:17.750 --> 29:19.680
you will do whatever I command.

29:21.960 --> 29:22.590
Leave.

29:24.720 --> 29:27.030
So much tension...

29:27.030 --> 29:28.680
You seemed quite happy

29:28.680 --> 29:30.310
just now in the main hall.

29:34.790 --> 29:36.050
Yes, Your Excellency.

29:36.260 --> 29:37.520
I'll take my leave now.

29:39.890 --> 29:40.350
I...

29:41.070 --> 29:41.620
Stop.

29:46.840 --> 29:48.100
Yes, Your Excellency.

29:49.150 --> 29:50.280
From this moment on,

29:50.550 --> 29:51.790
whatever Your Excellency commands,

29:51.790 --> 29:52.590
I will do.

29:53.190 --> 29:53.710
You...

29:58.480 --> 29:59.910
Are you deliberately playing hard

29:59.910 --> 30:01.110
to get and teasing me?

30:03.590 --> 30:04.960
No, I'm not.

30:06.170 --> 30:07.170
I wouldn't dare.

30:08.160 --> 30:09.400
I just feel...

30:10.440 --> 30:11.850
today Your Excellency

30:11.870 --> 30:13.350
seems rather strange.

30:14.440 --> 30:16.790
Not only is your mood so unpredictable,

30:17.370 --> 30:19.370
you're also hiding here alone

30:19.400 --> 30:21.320
studying the selection exam papers.

30:21.320 --> 30:22.420
Why is that?

30:44.740 --> 30:45.960
This is Zheng Shi's exam paper—

30:45.960 --> 30:47.590
I specifically had someone

30:48.050 --> 30:49.130
retrieve it.

30:50.640 --> 30:51.680
Zheng Shi's?

30:52.950 --> 30:54.880
Why did you request his exam paper?

30:57.240 --> 30:58.480
That Zheng Shi...

30:59.000 --> 31:00.800
though somewhat disagreeable,

31:00.940 --> 31:02.600
is still considered a talent.

31:05.400 --> 31:06.800
If he cannot be used by me,

31:07.590 --> 31:09.590
I must still remain cautious of him.

31:13.680 --> 31:14.640
Look closely—

31:18.310 --> 31:20.770
his general exam paper
is completely blank.

31:23.090 --> 31:24.540
Completely blank—

31:25.720 --> 31:27.650
and he still ranked twenty-third?

31:29.400 --> 31:30.510
Why do you remember his ranking

31:30.510 --> 31:31.720
so clearly?

31:32.880 --> 31:33.350
I...

31:37.750 --> 31:39.950
This is exactly where the mystery lies.

31:40.040 --> 31:42.070
A completely blank general exam paper,

31:42.070 --> 31:44.600
yet he achieved a high score
in the policy exam.

31:44.600 --> 31:45.950
It's almost as if the two papers

31:45.950 --> 31:48.550
were written
by completely different people.

31:48.600 --> 31:49.210
And look at

31:49.950 --> 31:51.480
this Current Affairs Essay—

31:51.480 --> 31:53.310
it's truly masterfully written.

31:53.310 --> 31:54.790
See how he argues

31:54.790 --> 31:56.790
that war cannot
ensure a nation's prosperity,

31:56.790 --> 31:59.390
and that hostilities
should therefore cease:

32:00.790 --> 32:02.190
"If that is not possible,

32:02.440 --> 32:04.270
one must resort to a secondary approach:

32:04.270 --> 32:05.720
evaluate it through five factors

32:05.720 --> 32:07.200
and verify it through calculation
to determine its true condition.

32:07.200 --> 32:08.060
First, the Way;

32:08.310 --> 32:09.680
second, Heaven;

32:09.680 --> 32:10.680
third, Earth;

32:10.680 --> 32:12.110
fourth, the Commander;

32:12.110 --> 32:13.200
fifth, Law."

32:25.830 --> 32:26.960
You're spacing out.

32:28.110 --> 32:30.170
I should never have shown this to you.

32:33.240 --> 32:34.820
Tomorrow at 5:30 AM,

32:35.480 --> 32:37.180
the newly admitted scholars shall come
to the Examination Office

32:37.180 --> 32:38.880
to receive their probationary assignments.

32:38.880 --> 32:39.720
Everyone,

32:39.720 --> 32:41.440
remember the time clearly.

32:41.440 --> 32:42.750
Come again tomorrow.

32:42.750 --> 32:44.150
That's all for today—dismissed.

32:44.150 --> 32:46.150
Let's go—disperse.

32:46.310 --> 32:47.640
Let's go back.

32:47.880 --> 32:56.490
[Announcement]

32:58.490 --> 33:13.550
[5:45 AM]

33:14.610 --> 33:16.570
Tomorrow at 5:45 AM,

33:16.680 --> 33:17.890
the newly admitted scholars shall come
to the Examination Office

33:17.890 --> 33:20.420
to receive their probationary assignments.

33:20.840 --> 33:21.770
By the way, Tian Xing,

33:21.770 --> 33:24.590
have you thought about how you're going
to spend your award money?

33:24.590 --> 33:25.550
Not yet.

33:25.550 --> 33:27.480
The Examination Office said they would
send someone home to notify my family,

33:27.480 --> 33:29.480
so I handed the reward money to them.

33:31.110 --> 33:32.240
You sent all that reward money

33:32.240 --> 33:33.550
back in one go?

33:35.440 --> 33:37.200
My family isn't well off.

33:37.200 --> 33:39.590
It hasn't been easy for them
to take me in all these years.

33:39.590 --> 33:40.400
No,

33:42.200 --> 33:44.000
what I mean is—

33:44.000 --> 33:46.240
sending such a big amount of reward money
all at once...

33:46.240 --> 33:47.510
Aren't you worried

33:47.510 --> 33:48.350
the escort

33:48.350 --> 33:50.410
might get any bad ideas along the way?

33:52.200 --> 33:53.930
That shouldn't happen, right?

33:54.240 --> 33:57.770
This is an official duty
supervised by the Examination Office.

33:57.880 --> 33:58.960
No matter which office it is,

33:58.960 --> 34:01.160
you should still write home to check.

34:03.270 --> 34:03.960
Alright.

34:06.960 --> 34:07.920
Thanks.

34:07.920 --> 34:09.110
Alright, Gao Ran, take care
on your way back.

34:09.110 --> 34:09.800
I'm off.

34:31.000 --> 34:32.429
It seems you have recovered well.

34:32.429 --> 34:33.510
Miss Wei.

34:38.510 --> 34:40.000
You always appear

34:40.000 --> 34:41.600
in the most unexpected ways.

34:42.550 --> 34:43.840
You bought so many good dishes—

34:43.840 --> 34:45.570
are you making them for Fan Yun?

34:47.070 --> 34:48.110
Then...

34:48.670 --> 34:50.540
Will you invite me to join you?

34:50.570 --> 34:52.969
You buy the ingredients,
I'll carry them;

34:53.960 --> 34:54.920
you cook,

34:54.920 --> 34:56.590
I'll keep you company while eating.

34:56.590 --> 34:57.590
Afterward,

34:59.110 --> 35:01.640
I'll take a look
at how your injury is healing.

35:05.440 --> 35:06.800
I'd better not.

35:06.800 --> 35:08.480
We're just having a simple family meal,

35:08.480 --> 35:09.840
nothing special.

35:13.360 --> 35:15.950
Don't you want to know

35:16.070 --> 35:17.710
why I came to see you this time?

35:17.710 --> 35:19.070
What is it?

35:19.630 --> 35:21.030
Actually, my family...

35:21.400 --> 35:22.510
we should

35:23.480 --> 35:24.880
go to your place

35:24.880 --> 35:26.540
and talk slowly while eating.

35:27.320 --> 35:28.520
Miss Wei,

35:28.540 --> 35:29.920
if you have something
to say, just say it.

35:29.920 --> 35:31.110
Let’s skip the meal.

35:31.800 --> 35:32.800
Why not?

35:33.670 --> 35:35.360
At least we're friends, aren't we?

35:35.360 --> 35:36.960
What's wrong with having a meal together?

35:36.960 --> 35:38.800
You don't have to be so cold

35:38.800 --> 35:40.150
every time you see me.

35:40.360 --> 35:41.480
I don't mean it that way.

35:41.480 --> 35:42.400
I'm just low in status
and busy with many matters.

35:42.400 --> 35:43.960
I really don't have the time
to deal with you.

35:43.960 --> 35:44.960
To deal with me...

35:50.920 --> 35:52.710
Yes, it is just me being dealt with.

35:52.710 --> 35:54.030
Every time I come to you—

35:54.030 --> 35:54.920
so to you,

35:54.920 --> 35:57.070
it must just feel like
you're dealing with me, right?

35:57.070 --> 35:58.800
I guess my brothers were right.

35:59.040 --> 36:00.700
I was just flattering myself.

36:00.900 --> 36:02.020
How could you

36:02.040 --> 36:03.440
ever truly care about me?

36:04.690 --> 36:05.810
Let me explain.

36:05.830 --> 36:06.270
I...

36:17.680 --> 36:18.320
You...

36:20.560 --> 36:21.850
Don't ever forget me.

36:22.510 --> 36:25.200
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

36:25.230 --> 36:26.440
♪ Over the whole town ♪

36:26.470 --> 36:28.970
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

36:29.110 --> 36:32.680
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

36:35.000 --> 36:37.470
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

36:37.500 --> 36:38.860
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

36:39.000 --> 36:41.590
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

36:41.710 --> 36:42.840
What's wrong with her today?

36:42.230 --> 36:45.710
♪ Strike out
on a fearless dream's frontier ♪

36:46.870 --> 36:50.180
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

36:50.210 --> 36:53.230
♪ A wisp of softness
tints your brow each day ♪
